<h1>Update on your ChooseRuby submission</h1>

<p>Hi <%= @entry.submitter_name || "there" %>,</p>

<p>
  Thank you for taking the time to submit a resource to ChooseRuby. After reviewing your submission, we're unable to publish it at this time.
</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Title:</strong> <%= @entry.title %></li>
  <li><strong>Type:</strong> <%= @entry.entryable_type.humanize %></li>
</ul>

<% if @comment.present? %>
<p>
  <strong>Feedback from our team:</strong><br>
  <%= simple_format(@comment) %>
</p>
<% else %>
<p>
  While we don't have specific feedback to share at this time, we carefully review all submissions to ensure quality and relevance for the Ruby community.
</p>
<% end %>

<p>
  We appreciate your interest in contributing to ChooseRuby. If you'd like to revise and resubmit this resource, or if you have other resources to share, please feel free to submit again.
</p>

<p>
  You can submit resources at <%= link_to "chooseruby.com", root_url %>.
</p>

